org.pepppt.core.storage

Class BatchIdsStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepppt.core.storage.BatchIdsStorage

  • public class BatchIdsStorage
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a list of EBIDs. It has an active EBID. It sort and remove the existing EBIDs in the list.
